{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01Qmcu12LPjNN6uhQuxPFbec","type":"tool_result","content":"  4770→- **Unattributed cost is the single largest bucket.** At $227.37 (26.0%), the \"unknown\" story bucket is larger than any real story. This needs attribution.\n  4771→- **Retro cost continues to grow.** At $103.25 (11.8%), retrospective generation costs more than actual development ($30.07). The retro file is now 4,629 lines — each new retro pays to read the entire thing.\n  4772→- **Verification phase dominance.** At 53.3% of total cost, verification is 15.7x more expensive than dev-story. Some of this is justified (rigorous quality gates), but the ratio warrants investigation.\n  4773→\n  4774→## 6. Lessons Learned\n  4775→\n  4776→- **First-pass success is achievable.** 41/41 ACs across 4 stories with zero rework proves the dev-then-review-then-verify pipeline works when story specs are clear.\n  4777→- **State writes need monotonic versioning.** This is the same lesson as every prior retro. Ralph's read-modify-write loop without version checking causes lost updates.\n  4778→- **Sprint-complete must be a hard exit.** Repeated across every retro entry. Ralph needs `if (done === total) exit(0)` at the top of each loop.\n  4779→- **Retro file growth is a cost multiplier.** At 4,629 lines, the file is the single largest context cost per retro session. Archiving old entries to separate files would cut this significantly.\n  4780→- **Subagent file read deduplication would save tokens.** The harness-run.md file was read 8 times across two subagents for the same story. A shared context or \"read once\" pattern would help.\n  4781→\n  4782→## 7. Action Items\n  4783→\n  4784→| Priority | Action | Status |\n  4785→|----------|--------|--------|\n  4786→| **P0** | Fix Ralph state corruption — add compare-and-swap or monotonic version to state writes | CRITICAL — 36+ occurrences |\n  4787→| **P0** | Add sprint-complete exit condition to Ralph's main loop | CRITICAL — each loop wastes ~$1.50-3 |\n  4788→| **P0** | Sprint is complete. Plan next sprint or close out. | CARRY FORWARD |\n  4789→| **P1** | Attribute the \"unknown\" cost bucket ($227.37, 26.0%) to specific phases/activities | CARRY FORWARD |\n  4790→| **P1** | Archive retro file — split into per-session files or rolling window (4,629 lines and growing) | CARRY FORWARD |\n  4791→| **P2** | Add subagent guideline: capture test output once, grep from capture | CARRY FORWARD |\n  4792→| **P2** | Add subagent guideline: deduplicate file reads across review+verification for same story | CARRY FORWARD |\n  4793→| **P2** | Fix 5 pre-existing BATS failures in all_tasks_complete suite | CARRY FORWARD |\n  4794→| **P3** | Clean up legacy `black.box` references in patches/templates | CARRY FORWARD |\n  4795→| **P3** | Clean up `1-1-foo` phantom story from tracking data ($24.35) | CARRY FORWARD |\n  4796→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01J7rgF7H1XXWzrAndxGStgP","session_id":"81cb382a-05ef-4370-9f23-d4277d76c153","uuid":"70053043-c14e-482d-8d92-4b757543b9f1","timestamp":"2026-03-28T12:40:43.222Z"}
